channel.title: Looking for some Coders
channel.description:
Hi guys,
I have an own server called X5-Scape ( its 317 and i used stabbingv4 as base ). But i wanna finish the source ( FINALLY )
And i can't code it all myself, so i'm looking for some coders. ( you need to be able to code 317 - 508 )
You will all get Owner rights in-game. ( i host but it isn't online yet )
I need 2 / 3 other coders.
Coders --> (1/4) Hosters --> (1/1) ( not 24/7 ) ( and not online yet )
So please help me;) it would be much faster so server can be earlier online for public!
From -- F4k4G
